_Sans Serif_ [reports](http://wearethebest.wordpress.com/2010/01/01/toi-jang-
geo-unite-to-give-peace-a-chance/) that two media giants – Jang from Pakistan
and The Times of India from India – have joined hands in a peace initiative
called ‘Aman ki Asha’ on the first day of the new year. The aim is to foster
greater understanding between people of the two countries and to give peace a
chance.

